The only way as said by youse123 is to disable self defense, exit kaspersky and then copy the two fitlib.dll and fitlin.ini to the program files folder. Start again Kaspersky, it will show till 2016. This procedure needs to be repeated every time your restart your pc but not when you hibernate.
